  "instructions": [
    "Heat the mini cocotte over medium heat.",
    "Spread butter on one side of each bread slice.",
    "Coat the buttered side with a thin layer of kombu cold extract.",
    "Add a drizzle of olive oil to the pan.",
    "Place the bread slices in the pan, buttered side down.",
    "Cook until the bottom is golden and crisp, about 3 minutes.",
    "Flip each slice, sprinkle with salt, pepper, shredded coconut, and toasted sesame seeds, then cook for 1 minute.",
    "Serve immediately while warm and crisp."
